Task: file-server
Section: server
Description: File server
 This task sets up your system to be a file server. It includes
 the samba server for Windows OS/2 or DOS clients, and a NFS server.
Packages:
 samba
 samba-doc
 smbclient
 swat
 smbfs
 # Is this the best one? Will it work out of the box for new debian
 # installs?
 nfs-kernel-server
